Name: Cookie Match: Enhanced Edition
About the game: Cookie Match is a game that everyone can enjoy. To match cookies and cookie cutters or icings, you will face different tricks in each room, that gives you a unique experience and entertainment. Clear all the stages and reveal cookies' true stories! How to play Move cookies to place them in the matching cookie cutters or the matching cookie icings. All the cookies move in the same direction as a set. Once a cookie meets the matching cutter or the matching cookie icing, the decoration is completed. Caution Butter packs are unmovable, like a wall. If a cookie hits the cutlery or a pigeon, then the cookie is fallen apart. Controls Control the direction with arrow keys or WASD (up / left / down / right) or touch / swipe R for the stage reset F for fullscreen on / off ESC for the previous page Backspace or Delete key for undo M for music on / off * Background music from Epidemic Sound
